      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Mr. Thomas A. McMillan, CIC Agent, This station, on 18 August 1947.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "On 7 July 1947, at approximately 10:10, while running up the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "XP-84 on the ground I noticed everyone was looking up into the air.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Off to the north about 10,000 to 12,000 feet altitude, was an object",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "that I assumed at first to be a weather balloon, but after looking at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "it for a while I noticed that it was oscillating in a forward whirling",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "movement without losing altitude. It was traveling about 200 to 225",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "MPH, and heading from west to east.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "The object was yellowish white in color and I would estimate that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "it was a sphere about 5 to 10 feet in diameter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "I did not have time to chase it in a P-80.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "This statement was given freely and voluntarily without any threats",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "or promises under duress. This statement consists of one (1) page, and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "is the truth to the best of my knowledge and belief.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
